values: Oh yes, ADVfilms did it again! I can't believe they dropped the evangelion anniversary pack project. After all the money saving I have gone through, all I will get is a nice sun exposition since ADV has left me hanging in the yard again. I feel so desappointed. On the other hand, Does anyone of you know where I can buy the 4 volume of Peacemaker Kurogane in japanese, I mean this version: not this one: It must have international shipping since I live in Panama. Also it would be great if the shipping cost were rational :p

Hi everyone! What a weekend hahahaha. This friday was my first obstetric turn, it was exiting but I ended up so tired -_- that now I have a cold. I feel so bad T_T I also went to the Anitour in Atlapa Convention Center. I think that the organization was pretty lame, so a message to the Rurouni-Slayers group: if you are going to organize an event please be more serious. Tomorrow is my obstetrics SUAGO rotation speak so wish me luck :p I want to rent the KareKano DVDs XD

ADV films will release this anniversary pack of Neon Genesis Evangelion which includes a lot of extras: +Contains every video extra ever created for Evangelion +Special commemorative art booklet +Limited-edition EVA 10th anniversary jacket +The Notenki Memoirs autobiography +Neon Genesis: Angelic Days manga +And more My favorite is the jacket. So this is my new obsession. I have already began to save my money because is quite expensive _-_ I hope ADV don't screwup as with Peace Maker Kurogane... In other subject, I feel that today is not a very happy day at least for now. I don't know I just feel tired of the routine. This week ends my period of practice in a pediatric hospital, and is very far from my house so my sleep time has reduced a lot. Maybe that is the reason of this feeling. Hopping for better days. Bye

Hi everyone! looooong time no see ya :D I have been quite busy since recently I moved, but now I want to keep journaling ^^ Today I'm happy to announce that I have become the owner of a gorgeous manga volumes: vol 1,2 and 3 of DNAngel. I have been in love with Yukiru Sugisaki's artwork since I had 14 years old, I now I have 3 of one of her best works DNAngel, I'm just tooooo happy to explain. So all I can say is if you don't know what the hell I'm talking about just go and google it, you will not be desappointed.

I'm back!!!
Hahaha, I feel so happy. 
Anyways today the exam was moved to July 5 _-_, yeah it was moved, all that effort for nothing.
Today I went to the gym again, but this time with my cousin, it was so much fun. 
Right now I'm so sleepy but I still want to log in PMK forum to say hi, and post a little.

From today to friday I'm gonna be quite busy since I have my second dermatology exam, which is very very difficult, so probably I'm going to desappear for this days. But remember if you miss me, I'm not dead I'm just studying.

PS: just trying to and some good humor to a very ugly situation. God please help me T_T.

Wow thanx to everyone who wished me luck on my exam, since I think I did pretty well, I'm so happy XD.
Today I started to go to the gymmnasium, but it seams like I'm only gonna be able to go on fridays and tusday since I'm too busy the rest of the week.
Anyways I think this is a good change And I hope to find more time for me and myself.
Everyone have a nice day ^^

I think we, all Peace Maker Kurogane fan's, have been very patient with ADV. How can you guys be so cruel. If you are not serious about releasing PMK then let other company do so. This post is to all PMK fans out there, you can take this big signature and fix it to the size you prefer, hope you like it. Wish me luck, tomorrow I have a Cardiology exam!
MMM well this is the first post. I have opened this journal with no particular purpose but I think this will be fun. ^^
